these things he said in himself, Even if I do not fear God, and do not regard man, 5 yet
because this widow gives me trouble, I will do her justice, lest, continuously coming,
she may bruise me.” 6 And the LORD said, “Hear what the unrighteous judge says:
7 and will God not execute justice to His chosen ones, who are crying to Him day andLuke 18:8
