23 and he, having heard these things, became very sorrowful, for he was exceedingly
rich. 24 And Jesus having seen him become very sorrowful, said, “How hardly will
those having riches enter into the Kingdom of God! 25 For it is easier for a camel to
enter through the eye of a needle, than for a rich man to enter into the Kingdom of
