suddenly there shone around him a light from Heaven, 4 and having fallen on the
earth, he heard a voice saying to him, “Saul, Saul, why do you persecute Me?” 5 And
he said, “Who are You, Lord?” And the LORD said, “I am Jesus whom you persecute;
