the sons of Israel; 16 for I will show him how many things he must suffer for My
Name.” 17 And Ananias went away, and entered into the house, and having put on
him [his] hands, said, “Saul, brother, the LORD has sent me—Jesus who appeared to
you in the way in which you were coming—that you may see again, and may be filled
with the Holy Spirit.” 18 And immediately there fell from his eyes as it were scales,
he also saw again instantly, and having risen, was immersed, 19 and having received
