their land to them by lot. 20 And after these things, about four hundred and fifty years,
He gave judges—until Samuel the prophet; 21 and thereafter they asked for a king, and
God gave to them Saul, son of Kish, a man of the tribe of Benjamin, for forty years;
22 and having removed him, He raised up to them David for king, to whom also having
