those of the [household] of Aristobulus; 11 greet Herodion, my relative; greet those of
the [household] of Narcissus, who are in the LORD; 12 greet Tryphaena, and Tryphosa,
who are laboring in the LORD; greet Persis, the beloved, who labored much in the
LORD. 13 Greet Rufus, the chosen one in the LORD, and his mother and mine, 14 greet
Asyncritus, Phlegon, Hermas, Patrobas, Hermes, and the brothers with them; 15 greet
