of the wrath of her whoredom she has given to all nations to drink.” 9 And a third
messenger followed them, saying in a great voice, “If anyone worships the beast and
his image, and receives a mark on his forehead or on his hand, 10 he also will drink
of the wine of the wrath of God that has been mingled unmixed in the cup of His
