said to me, “For this reason did you wonder? I will tell you the secret of the woman
and of the beast that [is] carrying her, which has the seven heads and the ten horns.
8 The beast that you saw: it was, and it is not, and it is about to come up out of the
abyss, and to go away to destruction, and those dwelling on the earth will wonder,
whose names have not been written on the Scroll of Life from the foundation of the
